00:48:32,651 --> 00:48:35,571
you wouldn't have to go through that, Dae Beom.

646
00:48:35,571 --> 00:48:37,921
You know it's not your fault, Yeo Reum.

647
00:48:37,921 --> 00:48:41,831
Because you came to Angok, I became sincerely happy.

648
00:48:41,831 --> 00:48:44,981
I don't want to create more sad situations.

