00:48:49,511 --> 00:48:52,001
Maybe he did the graffiti.

652
00:48:52,001 --> 00:48:53,472
We've installed the surveillance camera now.

653
00:48:53,472 --> 00:48:54,434
Who the heck are you?

654
00:48:54,434 --> 00:48:56,952
So we can catch the culprit if it happens again.
